        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2012-09-12 22:16:45.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nAlso is this the correct commit message? Could you add some explanation for the comment additions it is not clear how they affect an array overrun situation.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
    {
