      "message": "Patch Set 1: Fails\n\nTests received by maloo, run on el6/x86_64, el5/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/15583e4a-fd79-11e1-a1b4-52540035b04c).  Ran 2 tests.  1 tests failed: lustre-initialization-1.",
