      "date": "2012-09-14 11:22:17.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nUnfortunately, after several tests with Coverity I can say that replacing specific Coverity comments with macros is not working.\nComments added via macros are not seen by Coverity (probably because they are added by the preprocessor, so too late), and they have no effect.\n\nHowever, I will push a new version of the patch to improve the commit message.",
